Payment Receipt

Dear <%= @family.name %>,

Thank you for your payment! This email confirms we've received your payment for <%= @child.first_name %> <%= @child.last_name %>'s enrollment in <%= @program.name %>.

PAYMENT DETAILS
---------------
Amount: $<%= sprintf('%.2f', @payment.amount) %>
Payment Date: <%= @payment.payment_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
Payment Method: <%= @payment.payment_method.titleize %>
<% if @payment.payment_type == 'enrollment_fee' -%>
Type: Non-refundable Enrollment Fee
<% elsif @payment.payment_type == 'tuition' -%>
Type: Tuition Payment<%= " - Installment ##{@payment.installment_number}" if @payment.installment_number %>
<% end -%>

<% if @payment.notes.present? -%>
Notes: <%= @payment.notes %>

<% end -%>
A detailed receipt is attached to this email as a PDF.

<% if @payment.program_enrollment.enrollment_payment_plan -%>
<% plan = @payment.program_enrollment.enrollment_payment_plan -%>
<% total_paid = plan.total_paid + (plan.enrollment_fee_paid? ? plan.enrollment_fee : 0) -%>
<% remaining = plan.total_amount - plan.total_paid -%>
PAYMENT PLAN STATUS
-------------------
Plan: <%= plan.payment_plan.name %>
Total Tuition: $<%= sprintf('%.2f', plan.total_amount) %>
Total Paid: $<%= sprintf('%.2f', total_paid) %>
Remaining Balance: $<%= sprintf('%.2f', remaining) %>

<% if remaining > 0 -%>
<% next_installment = plan.next_installment -%>
<% if next_installment -%>
Next Payment: $<%= sprintf('%.2f', next_installment['amount']) %> due on <%= Date.parse(next_installment['due_date']).strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
Your account is paid in full!
<% end -%>
<% end -%>

If you have any questions about this payment or your account, please don't hesitate to contact us.

Thank you for being part of the Earthkin community!

Warmly,
The Earthkin Team
